{"tid":606454,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 每日只討論一個Topic (II)","createTime":"2018-03-26T13:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T10:45:59.000Z","uid":152322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33463d1ba856f0445236609a63dbc8d708d98ea0","tid":606454,"uid":152322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"上個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/582803/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/582803/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n事源小弟想開個Telegram Group<br />\n每日既討論內容只會圍繞一個主題<br />\n希望大家可以響充裕既時間下舒適地思考同討論<br />\n從而獲得一個不流於淺既對談及相交既經歷<br />\n<br />\n咁其實呢個小實驗已經差唔多玩完一圈<br />\n響開新一輪之前打算搵多幾位新朋友仔加入 暫定加多十個以內 <br />\n同樣地會用大家提供既題目玩一輪 再一齊做個review <br />\n謝謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScFR6XAuCI5RxqL4g3HqD_ac_sZaBfhGNVDqGIyCL9Ox9-R-Q/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScFR6XAuCI5RxqL4g3HqD_ac_sZaBfhGNVDqGIyCL9Ox9-R-Q%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3ca45fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScFR6XAuCI5RxqL4g3HqD_ac_sZaBfhGNVDqGIyCL9Ox9-R-Q/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"},{"pid":"6f5281025771f1afc63308af26aca0b552acc0a4","tid":606454,"uid":152322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefdaf58ba03db82583fb7511e04717c98d5282e","tid":606454,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"唔知你地想傾咩，anyway已填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a39beebd82982b047addda56aaa77ad19261b35","tid":606454,"uid":152322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cefdaf58ba03db82583fb7511e04717c98d5282e","tid":606454,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s